Author: honestis.network
Title: [Bounties] [ANN] [ preICO ] [ HONESTIS.NETWORK ]
Body: Important part for participants of bounty hunt clarified once more. 0,6x 3.2 = 1,92 % of tokens additional to created minimal Proof of Concept CAP for 100% for 1 ring delivery – PoC –the identity ring is 5000 ETC (Min cap generates  around 2 k $ for bounties outside translations and additional bounties) and 20 000 ETC for digital portable identity whole 3 rings and additional dapps. (twit, facebook, btt) 0,1% is for cryptocointalk and bitcoingarden . The preICO seed bonus apply to 2000 ETC and some seed declarations (+500 conversion rate) Maximum conversion rate in preICO is 2300 tokens for 1 ETC Minimal conversion during preICO is 1000 tokens for 1 ETC and this is basic conversion for preICO preICO ends in July 28th / beginning (14th ) of August, at least few days before ICO starts. In ICO starting end of July 28th / beginning (14th ) of August basic conversion rate is 800 and max with bonuses conversion is 600 + 800 = 1400 Estimated time of each ICO phase 8 weeks. The conversion will change to 500 after reaching cap of equivalent 3000 000 $ in ETC. The max cap for ICO formal stage will be equivalent of 10 000 000 $ in ETC. There will be option to set the final ICO phase by extending ICO and for 8 weeks  to gather funds for market growth only then conversion drops to 250 and max cap is 20 000 000 $ total Whole ICO campaign ends with September end - 10th November.    Conversion rate    preICO seed < 2000 ETC    preICO    ICO till 3 MLN    ICO till 10 MLN    ICO growth   Max        2300     1800           1400     1100       250   Min        1000     1000           800       500        250 Tokens can be received after each phase. Bounty hunters will be accepted once more after each phase, that will be not automatic.  Details bonus table will be on webpage and in smartcontract code.

HONESTIS.NETWORK  Great opportunity to change how world society communicate, trade and evolve by small steps of every individual. Introduction Social media it is a new technology, but  will grow, expand and penetrate dipper the market, as poor countries will develop. Right now the overdose of information which flow through social media is overwhelming. Social Media exists and grows. It is an interesting market with the great potential. Currently, data science is being used to reduce the cost of advertising, but unfortunately also at the expense of privacy, creating dangerous predictive capabilities and controlling the behaviour of the entire group, and above all the user in front of the computer, taking his time to activities he had not previously planned to do. Our data is a property owned by us, and our contacts and business connections are at our disposal, but we are giving them away for free, very often even paying for it. True social media such as viral marketing are limited by artificial technological processes and filters, so that the customer must advertise the idea or product through their information system. In turn their template way of transmitting information is extremely ineffective and even partially blocked in turn by private user software. This lack of idea to monetize user activity, rather than encouraging this activity (advertising), is an antisocial element and problem in the business model. A solution to this is Honestis network, restoring the social aspect of social media, giving users privacy and full freedom of mind, that kind of social media functionality will be used. Facilitated and fully accessible natural virals and social activity, building business relationships in a more professional and balanced acceptable way. At the same time having 1 account you can have totally different professional, social and political activity and be perceived as we want by the relevant audience. The intuitive, fast operation and activation of filters, encrusted and personalized business cards offer a number of new possibilities -they are more natural to people and, thanks to their multidimensional nature, they will make contacts easier for users with multidimensional relationships. Trust, respect and transparency with increased security of ourselves and our transactions. Honestis.Network is also to provide you with individual artificial assistant to help you through day, what is your design, to feel accomplished at every  step of your day to day journey. Assistant, which is heavily secure so may kept your most precious data, learns from you. Learns how to help you most effective to keep balance in your way of living and to cheer you and keep you always on track. Honestis.Network is your personal path, where you define how it crosses other people's paths in society, providing you with a safe journey around it and your individuality at a pace that suits you and your needs.  ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- -----------------------------------------  B O U N T I E S --------------------------------------------------------------------------------------  BOUNTY STRUCTURE  3.2 % off additional to collected donators generated tokens are reserved for bounties. So % above might change if one media will be much more active than another. Points earned even so are equally powerful.  1.1.   Details of rules for bounties in campaign:  Twitter Bounties Payment 0-99 followers: .01 Points/Reply positive comment with HASHTAGS 100-500 followers: .25 Points/ Reply positive comment with HASHTAGS or retweet 500 – 1000 followers: .5 Points/ Reply positive comment with HASHTAGS or retweet 1001 – 1500 followers: .75 Points/ Reply positive comment with HASHTAGS or retweet 1500- 2000 followers: 1.0 Points/ Reply positive comment with HASHTAGS or retweet 2001 – 2500 followers: 2.5 Points/ Reply positive comment with HASHTAGS or retweet 2500-5000: 6 Points/ Reply positive comment with HASHTAGS or retweet 5001+: 10 Points/ Reply positive comment with HASHTAGS or retweet  Rules 1. Follow our Twitter account  @HonestisN 2. Your Twitter must be active at the end of campaign and at least 7 days after as we need to calculate the Points 3. In a campaign you need to retweet at least 70% of our tweets there will be no more than 10 tweets a week or generate own with content related to cryptocurrency and with campaign tags Additional bonus for AVATAR-image and/or background: +2.5 Point/ Week if you wear our actual Avatar http://i.imgur.com/Wx2CSxl.png +2.5 Point/ Week if you wear our actual background http://i.imgur.com/IhwjfzX.png Acceptation of Participant is after filling this form : https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSff-Qsp9NymEH_YoT1BVya69nSLwTNrc4OIzTwPESREGakSOQ/viewform With SUBTITLE [ ICO SIGNATURE CAMAPIGN ] And links to your fb, twit, and btt talk profile. People with trust below 0 are not accepted. Other forums bounties: The same rules as for bitcointalk bounties apply to bitcoingarden.org forum and cryptocurrencytalk.com Except bonuses for signatures ( if no possible to display) and user ranks.
